Third-party dependencies
-------------------------

This repository names, but does not vendor, several third-party
dependencies:

- OCaml: `zarith` (GMP-backed exact rationals), `yojson` (JSON
  parsing), `sha` (SHA-256) -- installed via system packages
  (`libzarith-ocaml-dev`, `libyojson-ocaml-dev`, `libsha-ocaml-dev`),
  never copied into this repository as source.
- Python: Stone Soup (`stonesoup`, pinned only in the optional
  `requirements-stonesoup.txt`, MIT-licensed) -- an installed pip
  dependency, never vendored. See `docs/STONESOUP_THIRD_PARTY_NOTICE.md`
  for its own third-party licence/copyright notice, inherited unchanged
  from the upstream repository.

No other vendored or copied third-party source was found during the
2026-07-22 authorship/licensing audit that produced this file (see
`docs/UPSTREAM_PROVENANCE.md`).
